{"tid":1633840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"投降吧黑警，仲有條生路俾你同家人","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T02:40:02.000Z","uid":331650,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2d85e9fe9004ffc4288631d6c2a216f2dbf64ac2","tid":1633840,"uid":331650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:26:30.000Z","msg":"首<span style=\"color: green;\">十位</span>白警主動向傳媒供出警暴口供及證據，<span style=\"color: green;\">將獲考慮不加入國際制裁名單</span>。 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">請為你的家人著想</span>，真的想住在大灣區，不想讓仔女移民嗎? 光頭sir仔女上去都要讀<ins>國際學校</ins>，你就知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你自己深知你或你同胞的行為，正在違法，亦深知呢件事完左都係會被調查，所以你地先不停挑起事端唔想完結<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知道共產黨係點做野嗎? 共產黨要維穩，首先殺既搞既係知道真相既人，六四已告訴你，唔信就自己search，今年避得到，你退休避唔到，你全家都避唔到，黑警死全家呢樣野，黨會做得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><ins>十位身份將受保密</ins>。全港市民都等緊你。<span style=\"font-size: large;\">仲有，人權法十月就過，到時就幫唔到你。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Deadline: 10/10</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />形式: 自己錄影片+你張委任證+任何有利既證據(包括你既whatsapp/相片/影片)<br />\n建議傳媒: 立場，蘋果，外國傳媒，FreePress: <a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/contact-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2Fcontact-us&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4vaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=2164b762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/contact-us</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">供出公安者將另獲考慮</span><br />\n<br />\n如有補充或另外諗法，歡迎討論。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n解散警隊，刻不容緩。<br />\n早日投降，指證公安。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，反抗!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf1006ae87fc08b33d8d746006ca1a350eda55c","tid":1633840,"uid":331650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:28:48.000Z","msg":"P牌新手自推"},{"pid":"158c9d5ad19e6baf849